com.avaya.ic.sdk

Interface Party


  • public interface Party
    Represents an entity or participant involved in a MediaInteraction.

    Note: The name will vary depending upon the type of interaction. In case of chat, "name" represents the party name and in case of voice, "name" represents the phone number of the party (for the agent, it is the extension number).
